Package alien4cloud.ui.form.annotation

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    FormContentTypes  
    FormCustomType
    A custom form type, then it will not be introspected
    FormLabel
    Label is shown on generic form instead of property name
    FormPassword  
    FormProperties
    This annotation gives informations about which property will be included in the generated form, in the same time it gives the ordering of the properties in the form.
    FormPropertyConstraint
    This annotations define the constraint imposed on a form field
    FormPropertyDefinition
    This annotation is the mirror of PropertyDefinition.
    FormSuggestion
    This annotation contains information about suggestion that a property can have on the form

    FormTypes  
    FormValidValues
